    {
      "id": "insulation-roofing",
      "heading": {
        "en": "Self Tapping Screws for Exterior Wall Insulation and Color Steel Roof"
      },
      "body": {
        "en": "For <a href=\"/products#drywall-screws\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\">exterior wall insulation</a>systems (EIFS, ETICS), specialized long <a href=\"/products#drywall-screws\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\">self tapping screws</a>with large plastic disc <a href=\"/products#<a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\">washers</a></a></a></a></a>/a>\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\">washers</a></a></a></a></a>/a></a>(insulation retainers) are used to attach insulation boards to the substrate. The plastic disc (typically 50-60mm diameter) distributes load across the insulation without creating a thermal bridge. <a href=\"/products#self-drilling-screws\" class=\"te<a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\">washers</a></a></a></a></a>/a>ary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\">Drill tail screws<<a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\">washers</a></a></a></a></a>/a> href=\"/products#self-drilling-screws\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#self-drilling-screws\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#self-drilling-screws\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#self-drilling-screws\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#self-drilling-screws\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#self-drilling-screws\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#self-drilling-screws\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\">self drilling screws</a></a></a></a></a>/a></a>with extended drill flute) are designed for <a href=\"/products#self-drilling-screws\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\">color steel roof</a>and wall panel installations where the screw must penetrate through both the color steel sheet and any underlying insulation or purlin. The extended drill point (available in #2, #3, #4 drill capacities) ensures clean penetration without damaging the panel coating. EPDM bonded <a href=\"/products#<a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\">washers</a></a></a></a></a>/a>\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#wash<a href=\"/products#wash<a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\">washers</a></a></a></a></a>/a>ass=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\">washers</a></a></a></a></a>/a>=\"/products#<a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\">washers</a></a></a></a></a> class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\">washers</a></a></a></a></a>/a>ass=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products#washers\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\">washers</a></a></a></a></a>/a></a>/a> are essential for weather sealing in both applications.",
        "zh": "对于外墙保温系统（EIFS, ETICS），专用长自攻螺丝配合大塑料垫圈用于将保温板固定到基层。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "self-locking",
      "heading": {
        "en": "Self Locking and High Strength Self Tapping Screws"
      },
      "body": {
        "en": "<a href=\"/products#self-drilling-screws\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\">Self locking tapping screws</a>feature a serrated thread or flange design that provides additional resistance to loosening from vibration. The <a href=\"/products#self-drilling-screws\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\">hex head self locking</a>variant combines the high-torque drive capability of hex with locking thread features—common in automotive underbody panels and structural framing. <a href=\"/products\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\">High strength carbon steel</a>self tapping screws in Grade 8.8 or 10.9 equivalent are used where the screw itself must withstand high shear and tensile loads—not just fasten two pieces together but also carry structural load. These are common in solar panel mounting rails and industrial equipment brackets where the <a href=\"/products\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\"><a href=\"/products\" class=\"text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 underline underline-offset-2\">fastener</a></a></a></a></a>/a></a>is a structural element, not just a connector.",
        "zh": "自锁攻丝螺丝具有锯齿螺纹或法兰设计，提供额外的抗振动松动阻力。"
      }
    },
